   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Recto (hair side): ". . . on the field, and I know that my sister grieves concerning me." Paul said to him:  "I also for my part shall go with you. Why, O my brother, are you disturbed? But stay for this week . . . ";Verso (flesh side): " . . . [was] afraid to go to them lest it should be told to the duke and he should seize him, saying: "sacrifice." And after this, it was the twentieth of Parmoute, and the emperor Diocletian exiled a youth . . . "</ab>
         </div>
